The paper proposes an artificial intelligence predictive monitoring system for pipeline datasets, which involves classification and pattern recognition. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with security issues related to oil and gas pipelines, which could fall under the sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The proposed system also involves monitoring and control, which could be related to the sub-category of Systems and Control (cs.SI). Finally, the paper deals with the development of a new algorithm, which could be related to the sub-category of Software Engineering (cs.SE).
